    "context": "\"Inflicts [color=\" + this.Const.UI.Color.DamageValue + \"]\" + damage_armor_min + \"[/color] - [color=\" + this.Const.UI.Color.DamageValue + \"]\" + damage_armor_max + \"[/color] damage to armor\""
